ida Senate]]<br> from the 15th district|years=2001\u20132003}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Paula Dockery]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Lisa Carlton]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Member of the [[Florida Senate]]<br /> from the 24th district|years=2003\u20132009}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Thad Altman]]}}\n|-\n{{s-par|us-hs}}\n{{USRepSuccessionBox\n| state=Florida\n| district=15\n| before=[[Dave Weldon]]\n| after=[[Dennis A. Ross]]\n| years=2009\u20132013\n}}\n{{USRepSuccessionBox\n| state=Florida\n| district=8\n| before=[[Daniel Webster (Florida politician)|Daniel Webster]]\n| start=2013\n}}\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Jared Polis]]<br>D-[[Colorado]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=''[[List of current members of the United States House of Representatives by seniority|United States Representatives by seniority]]''|years=177th}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Phil Roe (politician)|Phil Roe]]<br>R-[[Tennessee]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{FL-FedRep}}\n{{USHouseCurrent}}\n{{U.S. Florida Representatives}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Posey, Bill}}\n[[Category:1947 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century American politicians]]\n[[Category:20th-century Methodists]]\n[[Category:21st-century American politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century Methodists]]\n[[Category:American people of Russian-Jewish descent]]\n[[Category:American United Methodists]]\n[[Category:Eastern Florida State College people]]\n[[Category:Florida city council members]]\n[[Category:Florida Republicans]]\n[[Category:Florida state senators]]\n[[Category:Members of the Florida House of Representatives]]\n[[Category:Members of the United States House of Representatives from Florida]]\n[[Category:People from Rockledge, Florida]]\n[[Category:Republican Party members of the United States House of Representatives]]"}]}}}}